'''Johann Sebastian Bach''' (* wazaka 21. <span>Marichi</span> <sup>Jul.</sup> <span>/</span> <span style="margin-left:-.1em">31.<nowiki><span typeof="mw:Entity">&</nowiki>nbsp;<nowiki></span></nowiki></span><span style="margin-left:-.1em">Marichi&nbsp;1685 <sup>greg.</sup></span> ku Eisenach, Saxony-Eisenach ; † 28. July 1750 mu Leipzig, Kursachsen ) anali German Wolemba, cantor, bwalo concertmaster, woyimba zeze ndi Baroque limba ndi harpsichord katswiri ku Thuringia . Johann Sebastian Bach anali m'modzi mwa akatswiri olemba nyimbo ku Europe. Anakhudza kwambiri olemba nyimbo ambiri kuyambira ku Mozart mpaka ku Schoenberg. Bach anali ndi ana 20; anayi a iwo adakhala olemba nyimbo otchuka.
